Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是学生会长久濑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.92,0:23:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,蜂蜜小熊
